			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				i was out on Erud's Crossing the other day killing wisps for the stones and happened to be hailed by a high lvl dwarf of unknown class who asked me if i could track a plague shark for him.  I noticed that the shark ususally follows the ships that come to port there.  i tracked it 3 times when the ship was in and none when the ship wasn't there. hope this helps.
				</font>
